## 📌 Features
- Headcount and Attrition Overview
- Employee Demographics Analysis
- Department-Wise Performance
- Gender Ratio and Diversity Metrics
- Tenure, Age, and Experience Breakdown
- Interactive Filters by Department, Gender, and Employment Status

## 📁 Folder Structure
- `Dataset/`: Contains the source data.
- `PowerBI_Report/`: Contains the `.pbix` file for Power BI.
- `Documentation/`: Includes metric definitions and project overview.
- `Images/`: Dashboard screenshots for preview.

## 🛠 Technologies Used
- Power BI Desktop
- DAX Measures
- Data Modeling (Relationships, Normalization)
- HR Domain KPIs
